{{en-verb|abus}}

# {{lb|en|transitive}} To put to a wrong use; to [[misapply]]; to use [[improperly]]; to [[misuse]]; to use for a wrong purpose or end; to [[pervert]] {{defdate|First attested around 1350 to 1470.}}
